{"tid":1401873,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根據懲教署的數字，現時在監獄共有一萬三千多名囚犯，比所有監獄的容量超出兩成多。","createTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T17:58:51.000Z","uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ddc17081dba38b8378a0b58786b84eecc63ffec8","tid":1401873,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:17:36.000Z","msg":"呢個會唔會係一個軟肋? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86191bbac6982a8ef13e0e438dd93ca2ff2f28f4","tid":1401873,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"嘩"},{"pid":"f427e3ada8c5f4f07ec8c9d6ef3c4111a20f2e33","tid":1401873,"uid":85437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:22:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會藉唔夠位為名 移交大陸監獄架⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516b577b9e5626e2372f38872039cb0a8be23047","tid":1401873,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">sorry 我 quote 錯左 95 年新聞黎</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大欖女子懲教所是近年擁擠問題較嚴重的監獄，重溫95年的報道。<br />\n現時囚犯的工作較以往輕鬆一點，因為在監獄內有過多人手去分擔工作。<br />\n根據懲教署的數字，現時在監獄共有一萬三千多名囚犯，比所有監獄的容量超出兩成多。其中以大欖女子懲教所的擁擠情況最嚴重，超額一倍有多。好像在這個工場，原先每班工作人數只是有五十人，現時差不多有一百人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://demo.news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/589b591f6db28c49298b4567/%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E6%93%81%E6%93%A0%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdemo.news.tvb.com%2Fprogrammes%2Fnewsfile%2F589b591f6db28c49298b4567%2F%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%258D%2584%25E6%2593%2581%25E6%2593%25A0%25E6%2583%2585%25E6%25B3%2581&d=DXsCe6mrroMB06wP0eqGVUn12mAFq1syGW6OSBl8LUM%3D&h=74107e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://demo.news.tvb.com/programmes/newsfile/589b591f6db28c49298b4567/%E7%9B%A3%E7%8D%84%E6%93%81%E6%93%A0%E6%83%85%E6%B3%81</a>"},{"pid":"f1eeb3aec19d85bebe295c535009e4704df43b6b","tid":1401873,"uid":86345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:58:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">此post已完</span>"}]}